name: You pick the Size we pick the pocket
description:
You Pick the Size/Colour of the T-shirt and we'll pick a random Pocket for you! pockets that can be picked are in the picture. 

Info:
Unique handmade Unisex Pocket T-shirts made by One Of The Gang.
T-shirts are 100% cotton and come Pre-shrunk. 

Shipping: 
Please allow 1-3 weeks for shipping.

Size Chart (width x length):
Small - 18 x 28 inches 
Medium - 20 x 29 inches 
Large - 22 x 30 inches 
(Double the width to get the Chest Size.)
